The Octane Level will start at 100% and decrease if there is persistant knock sum present. the Octane Level % is used as part of adjustment to the Timing (% between Low Octane Timing ecu map and High Octane Timing ecu map) to help protect the engine from excessive knock, normally caused by lean fuel conditions (excessive heat), or bad octane fuel.
